{"tid":1268310,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:47:46.000Z","uid":235644,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17d922246e0faa030846acb26a29920730679215","tid":1268310,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"知道琴日又有一位烈士離開左我地, 我同你地一樣都係好難過,<br />\n亦都明白大家好想有一個空間去放負能量, 但麻煩大家係出POST放既時候要諗一諗,<br />\n其實你地一舉一動有好多人留意住, 可能你地一句既說話就有人會諗埋一二面,<br />\n真心唔想見到有自殺潮, 再出現第3, 4, 5...個烈士既...<br />\n<br />\n如果你地真係有需要有個對象分享, 可以試下去:<br />\n<br />\n[我係準社工/樹窿 入黎睇睇]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1266492/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1266492/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[個心好痛 想講又講唔到 入黎傾吓偈]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1266068/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1266068/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住, 講野1999, 希望大家可以撐住, 守護好香港,<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地一個都不能少</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2dc03e8acd708a0e4de0a3ec0ef393d2b1bce6ca","tid":1268310,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbffa5cba9648e0c1e6244977798011d1326cb88","tid":1268310,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"dd079a0c5a246ce6eb9d90dbe727d67109247d92","tid":1268310,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9b8c0ff5cec37717270f38a334fb5d78b5d819e","tid":1268310,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17399c13005fceacf98394e70619b423b138f089","tid":1268310,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"推啊!"},{"pid":"03296e537